| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4229 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e8d2ec40-cfe3-5810-b4dc-56a73397ec90"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
